comment: I won't see ya at AC Tom. Hope you have a great time.

not gonna lie, looks a little burnt
That's just some of the seasonings on the crispy chicken skin.
I think that's the cumin that darkened the most.
But the rest is fine, only cooked for about a half hour.
gets crispy on the outside, but lets everything stay juicy on the inside.
And because part of the prep is crushing the chest, it lies nice and flat/thin, so everything cooks evenly/quickly.
Legit question here: I’m emailing a company to close an account with them. Does it make ANY SENSE to anyone else why they’d call me in response?
to confirm you are the real owner of the account
It’s just it doesn’t match the customer service number on the website
Dunno if I would trust. Still, it may not always match.
You can always contact the site support and ask them about it
I'm sure they'd have no problems verifying the number that called you.
cuz if that number is NOT them and is asking about your info, then there's something bad going on
cuz someone would have to know that you contacted them and know your number in order to call you back
